select `admin_permissions`.*, `admin_role_permissions`.`role_id` as `pivot_role_id`, `admin_role_permissions`.`permission_id` as `pivot_permission_id` from `admin_permissions` inner join `admin_role_permissions` on `admin_permissions`.`id` = `admin_role_permissions`.`permission_id` where `admin_role_permissions`.`role_id` in (1, 9)

select `admin_permissions`.*, `admin_user_permissions`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `admin_user_permissions`.`permission_id` as `pivot_permission_id` from `admin_permissions` inner join `admin_user_permissions` on `admin_permissions`.`id` = `admin_user_permissions`.`permission_id` where `admin_user_permissions`.`user_id` = 1

select count(*) as aggregate from `organisations` where `relationship_type` = 'opd'
select region_id, count(*) as count from `organisations` where `relationship_type` = 'du' group by `region_id`
select region_id, count(*) as count from `organisations` where `relationship_type` = 'opd' group by `region_id`
select `membership_type`, count(*) as count from `organisations` where `relationship_type` = 'du' group by `membership_type`
select `membership_type`, count(*) as count from `organisations` where `relationship_type` = 'opd' group by `membership_type`
select distinct `sex` from `people` where `sex` is not null

select `districts`.`name` as `district`, count(*) as count, `people`.`sex` as `sex` from `people` inner join `districts` on `people`.`district_id` = `districts`.`id` where `people`.`sex` is not null and `people`.`sex` <> 'N/A' group by `districts`.`name`, `people`.`sex`
